      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "BRING YOUR BEST (4) has been in super consistent form recently with two minors on end before missing the frame latest finishing fourth (19.77) at Healesville. Form at the trip sound including 15 wins. Has ability and can bounce back. FIELD OF ANGELS (3) turned spotting a big start finishing seventh (23.19) last time in a Grade 5 at Warragul. Deserves plenty of respect. RATTLIN' ROUND (2) turned in a plain run last time when eighth at Healesville over 300m behind Daintree Dazzler (17.50) in a Grade 5. Yet to win out of this box but has been in the placings two times from four starts. Great chance to atone. IRISH CARLA (1) cannot be underestimated.",
